high_descs: Turn around and walk to the head of lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Put the head of lettuce in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Walk to the small black side table to the left of the sink.
Put the head of lettuce on the right side of the side table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned head of lettuce on a small side table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the left just right of the stove.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Take a step to the left.
Put the lettuce on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed head of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Move to the table with the lettuce on it.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Move over to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink and turn on the water.
Pick up the lettuce and bring it to the black table to the left of the sink.
Place the lettuce on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward then turn left after you pass the stove and walk to the white table
Pick up the lettuce that is on the white table
Turn right and walk to the sink
Place the lettuce into the sink and then turn on the faucet to rinse the lettuce, then turn off the faucet and pick up the lettuce
Move to the left of the sink to the black shelf
Place the lettuce on the top shelf
anns.task_desc: Place rinsed lettuce on a shelf

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the sink, then hang a left and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the table.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Put the head of lettuce in the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean head of lettuce.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the black shelving unit in between the trash bag and counter.
Put the clean head of lettuce on top of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the counter on the left.
Pick up the lettuce.
Turn around and head to the sink on the right.
Put the lettuce in the sink, turn on the water to wash it, and turn it off, then pick up the lettuce.
Turn and head to the left side of the counter towards the black table.
Place the lettuce on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Wash the lettuce in the sink.
